summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to occupational utility taxes; amending Seattle Municipal Code Sections 5.48.010, .020, .030, .050, .055, .060, .070, .072, .080, .090, .100, .110, .120, .140, .150, .160, .170, .200, and .210; adding Sections 5.48.095, .135, and .220; repealing Section 5.48.130, because it has been reworded and renumbered as 5.48.150; repealing 5.48.190 because it has been renumbered as 5.48.030(D) and (E); and repealing 5.48.250 because it has been renumbered as 5.48.070(D).
